# Intentionally empty.
#
# Cloudflare Deploy to Cloudflare reads `.dev.vars.example` as deploy-time secret prompts.
# Fresh self-hosted Nanites deploys should not ask for any runtime secrets up front; `/setup`
# generates the auth cookie secret and customer-owned GitHub App credentials after Cloudflare
# ownership is verified.
#
# For local development details, see `docs/development.md`.
